        <text>
            <body>
                
                                        <p>Ego <persName key="d1e14057" xml:id="d1e138918">Bernardus, dictus abbas
                                <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e138920">Fonteneti</orgName>
                        </persName>, et ego <persName key="d1e14064" xml:id="d1e138923">Margarita,
                            priorissa <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281651" xml:id="d1e138925">Juliaci</orgName>
                        </persName>, no<lb n="2" break="no" corresp="#A2"/>tum <lb n="2" corresp="#A1"/> fieri volumus presentibus pariter et futuris quod
                        querela que vertebatur <lb n="3" corresp="#A2"/> inter domum <lb n="3" corresp="#A1"/>
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e138936">Fonteneti</orgName> et
                        domum <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281651" xml:id="d1e138939">Juliaci</orgName>
                        super pasturis de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325023" xml:id="d1e138942">Saneveto</placeName>, quas pars utra<lb n="4" break="no" corresp="#A2"/>que partim guage<lb n="4" break="no" corresp="#A1"/>ria partim elemosina
                        possidebat, de utriusque capituli assensu <lb n="5" corresp="#A2"/> hoc modo
                        pacificata <lb n="5" corresp="#A1"/> est. Videlicet quod animalia seu
                        peccora utriusque domus eisdem <lb n="6" corresp="#A2"/> pasturis in commune
                            uten<lb n="6" break="no" corresp="#A1"/>tur secundum possibilitatem
                        utriusque domus. Si vero pro <app>
                            <lem wit="#A1">adquisitione</lem>
                            <rdg>acquisitione</rdg>
                        </app>
                        <lb n="7" corresp="#A2"/> pasturarum <lb n="7" corresp="#A1"/> quas utrique
                        in vadimonio habemus expensas fieri contigerit, per medium per<lb n="8" break="no" corresp="#A2"/>solventur, <lb n="8" corresp="#A1"/> et <app>
                            <lem wit="#A1">adquisitio</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#A2">acquisitio</rdg>
                        </app> ipsa assensu utriusque partis fiat. Carte vero quas de eisdem <lb n="9" corresp="#A2"/> pasturis <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281651" xml:id="d1e138980">Juli<lb n="9" break="no" corresp="#A1"/>acenses</orgName> habent, huic compositioni obviare non poterunt. Hec
                            autem<lb n="10" corresp="#A2"/> communitas solun<lb n="10" break="no" corresp="#A1"/>modo de pasturis et de aasentiis aquarum facta est.
                        Ceterum de fun<lb n="11" break="no" corresp="#A2"/>do terre in pratis et
                        terris pre<lb n="11" break="no" corresp="#A1"/>fati territorii prout queque
                        domus sibi <app>
                            <lem wit="#A1">adquisivit</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#A2">acquisivit</rdg>
                        </app> emptione <lb n="12" corresp="#A2"/> vel elemosina vel <app>
                            <lem wit="#A1">ad<lb n="12" break="no" corresp="#A1"/>quirere</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#A2">acquirere</rdg>
                        </app>poterit, sine contradictione alterius sibi adquirat. Et quia <lb n="13" corresp="#A2"/> sanctimoniales in pasturarum <lb n="13" corresp="#A1"/>
                        <app>
                            <lem wit="#A1">adquisitione</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#A2">acquisitione</rdg>
                        </app> amplius se gravari conquerebantur, de be<lb n="14" break="no" corresp="#A2"/>neficio ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e139022">Fonteneti</orgName>
                        <lb n="14" corresp="#A1"/> XXX<hi rend="superscript">ta</hi>. libras
                        provinensium habuerunt. Hujus rei testes sunt : <persName key="d1e14070" xml:id="d1e139030">Gervasius came<lb n="15" break="no" corresp="#A2"/>rarius</persName>, <persName key="d1e14076" xml:id="d1e139035">Ysenbardus <lb n="15" corresp="#A1"/> capellanus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281651" xml:id="d1e139039">Juliaci</orgName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14082" xml:id="d1e139042">Hugo</persName> et
                            <persName key="d1e14088" xml:id="d1e139045">Willelmus cellerarii
                                <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e139047">Fonten(eti)</orgName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14094" xml:id="d1e139050">Josbertus de <lb n="16" corresp="#A2"/>
                            <foreign>Masi</foreign>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e14101" xml:id="d1e139057">Johannes <lb n="16" corresp="#A1"/> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325023" xml:id="d1e139061">Saneveto</placeName>
                        </persName>, milites, <persName key="d1e14107" xml:id="d1e139064">Theobaudus
                            prepositus <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324487" xml:id="d1e139066">Montis
                                Barri</placeName>
                        </persName>. Quod totum <lb n="17" corresp="#A2"/> ut ratum habe<lb n="17" break="no" corresp="#A1"/>atur in posterum, sigillis nostris hanc
                        cartulam munivimus<lb n="18" corresp="#A2"/>. Anno Verbi incar<lb n="18" break="no" corresp="#A1"/>nati millesimo ducentesimo.</p>
                
